## Test Results Summary

### Test Case 1 — Standard Flow (High Severity)
- Input: "There is a water leak" → Building C → High → Description
- Result: **PASS** — all 3 parameters captured, confirmation returned with reference ESG-2026-0047

### Test Case 2 — Critical Escalation
- Input: "There is a water leak" → Building A → Critical
- Result: **PASS** — bypassed Description page, routed directly to Escalation page, reference ESG-CRIT-2026-0012 returned

